DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260310T150000
UID:097063eb16ecf49c54d091cc370741b7@montclairfilm.org
DESCRIPTION:In 1930s Chicago\, groundbreaking scientist Dr. Euphronious br
 ings a murdered young woman back to life to be a companion for Frankenstei
 n's monster. What happens next is beyond what either of them could ever ha
 ve imagined.
LOCATION:Bellevue 1\, 260 Bellevue Avenue\, Montclair\, NJ 07043
URL:https://montclairfilm.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FRk
